{"tid":1633351,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：連登巴打英文game 向國際宣傳反送中 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:03:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5add8599baf7c53af965e214c372a89b65f03a83","tid":1633351,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191007/20782604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F20782604&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4ltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=ccea2fae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F20782604&h=7f85a1ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191007/20782604</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：連登巴打英文game<br />\n向國際宣傳反送中 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191007/large/1570381997_e1a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570381997_e1a1.jpg&h=4f09f9f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次反送中運動中，國際文宣真係好厲害，呢個當然係連登攬炒巴同佢團隊嘅功勞，但亦有連登巴打提過，單靠海外廣告可能未必夠，特別係對外國年輕人，網上文宣都好重要，有連登巴竟然整咗個英文嘅角色扮演手遊，等外國人可以透過呢個game，由6月9日反送中運動開始，了解港人點樣走過成個抗爭運動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文字RPG 玩家買裝備<br />\n<br />\n呢隻叫「The Revolution of Our Times I」嘅文字RPG ，主要用文字方式，由你扮演不同角色做不同決定，去體驗由6.9開始點樣參與運動，而每個決定都有機會影響故事嘅發展同選擇，例如選擇走佬離開香港，就冇得選擇去前線，遊戲亦有得買裝備，提升力量去前線，又有不同任務可以打。<br />\n<br />\n創作呢隻game巴打話，搞呢隻game係為爭取國際嘅支持，因為佢想全世界嘅人都有機會了解、體驗反送中運動，但佢係冇可能買幾萬張機票，叫晒全世界人嚟香港參與，所以就寫咗呢隻以文字為主嘅RPG，希望可以畀所有人都有機會參加呢場時代革命，體驗一下香港人由6月9號開始所經歷過嘅嘢。而呢隻game叫「The Revolution of Our Times I」，因為佢預仲有第二同第三集，暫時就只有android版，可以去Google Play store下載遊戲，巴打仲話遊戲嘅八成收入，每個月尾會捐畀星火。<br />\n<br />\n李八方 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：建制區選海報 人瘦logo細 (李八方)"},{"pid":"20edd5ca22e7a829e483ad6eee0ccb093cba4c2e","tid":1633351,"uid":295053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7567063e1f2e5a0241603479435dcaa6c91b7aca","tid":1633351,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:07:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支持</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=story.hk.hkmovement\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dstory.hk.hkmovement&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4ltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=ac2c4dea\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=story.hk.hkmovement</a>"},{"pid":"5175e394328056a7df62f9f694819086dcc93ab4","tid":1633351,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">隻game俾人隊落架，快開新post救佢!</span>"},{"pid":"de1d8ce76a9083ca02b2c8b845c1a85e09b3be1b","tid":1633351,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇人救下佢?</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/10/revolution-times-hong-kong-protester-role-playing-game-suspended-google-play-store/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F10%2Frevolution-times-hong-kong-protester-role-playing-game-suspended-google-play-store%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4ltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=14f15377\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/10/revolution-times-hong-kong-protester-role-playing-game-suspended-google-play-store/</a>"}]}